r |\n54\t| `duskyRose` | `#FBC4E0` | Secondary accent, Mindfulness icon |\n55\t| `nightMint` | `#34D399` | Tertiary, success states |\n56\t| `deepTwilight` | `#1E1B2E` | Card backgrounds |\n57\t| `nightSky` | `#13111C` | Scaffold background |\n58\t| `softPearl` | `#F3F4F6` | Primary text |\n59\t| `mutedSilver` | `#9CA3AF` | Secondary text, descriptions |\n60\t| `deepBorder` | `#2D2B3A` | Card borders |\n61\t| `charcoalSurface` | `#252336` | Bottom nav background, card surfaces |\n62\t\n63\t### Typography (Google Fonts — Nunito)\n64\t\n65\t| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n66\t|---|---|---|---|---|\n67\t| `displayLarge` | 32sp | 700 | 40sp | User name display |\n68\t| `headlineMedium` | 24sp | 700 | 32sp | Section headers |\n69\t| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | 28sp | AppBar title |\n70\t| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Card titles |\n71\t| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | 24sp | Body text |\n72\t| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Secondary text, descriptions |\n73\t| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | 20sp | Button text, chip labels |\n74\t| `caption` | 12sp | 400 | 16sp | Badges, timestamps |\n75\t\n76\t### Spacing Rhythm (base 8dp)\n77\t\n78\t| Token | Value |\n79\t|---|---|\n80\t| `xxs` | 4dp |\n81\t| `xs` | 8dp |\n82\t| `sm` | 12dp |\n83\t| `md` | 16dp |\n84\t| `lg` | 24dp |\n85\t| `xl` | 32dp |\n86\t| `xxl` | 48dp |\n87\t\n88\t### Corner Radius\n89\t\n90\t| Token | Value |\n91\t|---|---|\n92\t| `sm` | 8dp |\n93\t| `md` | 12dp |\n94\t| `lg` | 16dp |\n95\t| `full` | 999dp |\n96\t\n97\t### Motion\n98\t\n99\t| Token | Duration | Curve |\n100\t|---|---|---|\n101\t| `durationShort` | 200ms | `Curves.easeOut` |\n102\t| `durationMedium` | 300ms | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n103\t| Stagger delay | 50ms between items | — |\n104\t\n105\t### Elevation\n106\t\n107\t| Token | Usage |\n108\t|---|---|\n109\t| `level0` | Scaffold background |\n110\t| `level1` | Cards, bottom nav |\n111\t| `level2` | FAB, bottom sheets |\n112\t\n113\t---\n114\t\n115\t## 6. Layout Rules\n116\t\n117\t### Scaffold Structure\n118\t\n119\t- `Scaffold` with `SingleChildScrollView` as body (simple card list, no slivers needed)\n120\t- `AppBar`: title \"Profile\", no leading (tab screen), transparent background\n121\t- `BottomNavigationBar`: visible (4 tabs, index 3 = Profile active)\n122\t- No FAB on Profile tab screen\n123\t- Safe area: 12dp top padding for status bar, 80dp bottom for nav + home indicator\n124\t\n125\t### AppBar Behavior\n126\t\n127\t- Transparent background blending to `lavenderTint`\n128\t- Title: \"Profile\" (SemiBold 20sp, `deepGraphite`)\n129\t- No back button (tab screen)\n130\t- No trailing actions\n131\t\n132\t### Body Layout\n133\t\n134\t- `SingleChildScrollView` as body\n135\t- `Padding` with 16dp horizontal\n136\t- `Column` with `mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min` containing sections\n137\t- 24dp vertical spacing between sections\n138\t- Bottom padding: 100dp to clear bottom nav\n139\t\n140\t---\n141\t\n142\t## 7. Sections\n143\t\n144\t### Section 1: Profile Header (Avatar + Name)\n145\t\n146\t**Description:** User avatar with gradient background, name, and due date preview.\n147\t\n148\t**Widget Type:** `Column` with centered content, wrapped in `SliverToBoxAdapter`\n149\t\n150\t**Layout:** Centered column at top of scrollable content.\n151\t\n152\t**Components:**\n153\t- Avatar container (80dp diameter) with gradient fill (`lavenderBloom` to `blushRose`)\n154\t- User initial or emoji inside avatar circle\n155\t- User name (`displayLarge`, `deepGraphite`)\n156\t- Due date subtitle (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`) — from `PregnancyProfileProvider`\n157\t- Edit profile button (text button, `lavenderBloom`)\n158\t\n159\t**Data Requirements:**\n160\t- `name` from `UserPreferencesProvider`\n161\t- `dueDate` from `PregnancyProfileProvider`\n162\t\n163\t**Interactive Elements:**\n164\t- Tap edit profile button → `context.push('/settings')` (Profile section)\n165\t- Tap avatar → no action (decorative)\n166\t\n167\t---\n168\t\n169\t### Section 2: Mindfulness Link Card\n170\t\n171\t**Description:** Navigation card leading to guided breathing exercises and stretching guides.\n172\t\n173\t**Widget:** `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback.\n174\t\n175\t**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, `Row` with icon left, text right, chevron trailing.\n176\t\n177\t**Components:**\n178\t- 48dp circular icon container with `blushRose` at 20% opacity fill\n179\t- Icon: `Icons.self_improvement` (24sp, `blushRose`)\n180\t- Title: \"Mindfulness\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n181\t- Description: \"Breathing exercises, stretching, relaxation\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n182\t- Trailing: `Icons.chevron_right` (24sp, `stoneGrey`)\n183\t\n184\t**Data Requirements:** None (static navigation)\n185\t\n186\t**Interactive Elements:**\n187\t- Tap card → `context.push('/mindfulness')`\n188\t- Scale feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms return\n189\t\n190\t---\n191\t\n192\t### Section 3: Settings Link Card\n193\t\n194\t**Description:** Navigation card leading to app settings and preferences.\n195\t\n196\t**Widget:** `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback.\n197\t\n198\t**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, `Row` with icon left, text right, chevron trailing.\n199\t\n200\t**Components:**\n201\t- 48dp circular icon container with `lavenderBloom` at 15% opacity fill\n202\t- Icon: `Icons.settings_outlined` (24sp, `lavenderBloom`)\n203\t- Title: \"Settings\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n204\t- Description: \"Notifications, due date, data export\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n205\t- Trailing: `Icons.chevron_right` (24sp, `stoneGrey`)\n206\t\n207\t**Data Requirements:** None (static navigation)\n208\t\n209\t**Interactive Elements:**\n210\t- Tap card → `context.push('/settings')`\n211\t- Scale feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms return\n212\t\n213\t---\n214\t\n215\t### Section 4: App Info Card (About)\n216\t\n217\t**Description:** Minimal card showing app version.\n218\t\n219\t**Widget:** `Card` (non-interactive, display only).\n220\t\n221\t**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding.\n222\t\n223\t**Components:**\n224\t- App name: \"Baby Bump\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n225\t- Version text: \"Version 1.0.0\" (`caption`, `stoneGrey`)\n226\t- Privacy policy link text button\n227\t\n228\t**Data Requirements:** None (static content)\n229\t\n230\t**Interactive Elements:** None (display only)\n231\t\n232\t---\n233\t\n234\t## 8. Data\n235\t\n236\t### Entities Consumed on This Screen\n237\t\n238\t| Entity | Provider | Fields Used |\n239\t|---|---|---|\n240\t| `UserPreferences` | `UserPreferencesProvider` | `name` |\n241\t| `PregnancyProfile` | `PregnancyProfileProvider` | `dueDate` |\n242\t\n243\t### State Operations\n244\t\n245\t- **Read** `name` for Profile Header display name\n246\t- **Read** `dueDate` for Profile Header due date subtitle\n247\t\n248\t### Provider Integration\n249\t\n250\t```dart\n251\t// In ProfileScreen build method:\n252\tfinal userPrefs = ref.watch(userPreferencesProvider);\n253\tfinal pregnancyProfile = ref.watch(pregnancyProfileProvider);\n254\t```\n255\t\n256\t---\n257\t\n258\t## 9. Motion\n259\t\n260\t### Entry Animations\n261\t\n262\t- Screen loads with fade-in: 300ms, `Curves.easeOut`\n263\t- Header avatar has subtle scale-in: 200ms from 95% to 100%\n264\t- Cards use staggered entry: 100ms delay between each card, 300ms fade per card\n265\t- Total stagger duration: 600ms for all four sections\n266\t\n267\t### Interactive Feedback\n268\t\n269\t- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms ease-out return\n270\t- Bottom nav indicator: 200ms ease-in-out glide between tab positions\n271\t\n272\t### Anti-Motion\n273\t\n274\t- All animations respect `MediaQuery.disableAnimations`\n275\t- `prefers-reduced-motion` media query honored — when enabled, skip all animations\n276\t\n277\t---\n278\t\n279\t## 10. Accessibility\n280\t\n281\t### Semantic Labels\n282\t\n283\t| Element | Semantic Label |\n284\t|---|---|\n285\t| AppBar | `'Profile screen'` |\n286\t| Avatar | `'User profile picture'` |\n287\t| Name display | `'User name: ${userName}'` |\n288\t| Due date display | `'Due date: ${formattedDate}'` |\n289\t| Edit profile button | `'Edit profile, double tap to open settings'` |\n290\t| Mindfulness card | `'Mindfulness, double tap to open mindfulness screen'` |\n291\t| Settings card | `'Settings, double tap to open settings screen'` |\n292\t| Bottom nav items | Built-in semantics from `NavigationBar` |\n293\t\n294\t### Focus Order\n295\t\n296\t1. Avatar circle\n297\t2. User name\n298\t3. Due date subtitle\n299\t4. Edit profile button\n300\t5. Mindfulness card\n301\t6. Settings card\n302\t7. About card\n303\t8. Bottom navigation items (in order: Home, Browse, Library, Profile)\n304\t\n305\t### Contrast Notes\n306\t\n307\t- `lavenderBloom` (#7C3AED) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~5.2:1 (AA compliant)\n308\t- `blushRose` (#F9A8D4) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~3.8:1 (AA borderline — used for icon backgrounds)\n309\t- `deepGraphite` (#1F2937) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~12:1 (AAA compliant)\n310\t- `stoneGrey` (#6B7280) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~4.7:1 (AA borderline — used for descriptions only)\n311\t- Active bottom nav text uses `lavenderBloom` (5.2:1), inactive uses `stoneGrey` (4.7:1)\n312\t\n313\t### Touch Target Compliance\n314\t\n315\t- All cards: full card area, minimum 56dp height\n316\t- Icon containers: 48dp diameter\n317\t- Edit profile button: 48dp minimum height\n318\t- Avatar: 80dp diameter (decorative, no interaction beyond visual)\n319\t- All interactive elements meet 48dp minimum touch target\n320\t\n321\t### Screen Reader Support\n322\t\n323\t- `AnnounceRouteChange` for tab switches\n324\t- Live region on profile name: \"Profile screen, ${userName}\"\n325\t\n326\t---\n327\t\n328\t## 11. Anti-Patterns\n329\t\n330\t**Do Not:**\n331\t- Add a FAB to Profile tab screen (tab screens don't have FABs per UX.md)\n332\t- Use `CustomScrollView` with slivers (not needed for simple card list — use `SingleChildScrollView`)\n333\t- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only for content cards)\n334\t- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)\n335\t- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito\n336\t- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp\n337\t- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text\n338\t- Add more than the 4 defined sections (header, mindfulness, settings, about)\n339\t- Use hero animations (simple push navigation with no shared elements)\n340\t- Add elevation shadows beyond level1 for cards (soft shadow only)\n341\t- Place critical actions below the thumb zone\n342\t- Use hard-coded user name — derive from `UserPreferencesProvider.name`\n343\t\n344\t---\n345\t\n346\t## 12. Navigation Dependencies\n347\t\n348\t| Destination | Route | Navigation Type |\n349\t|---|---|---|\n350\t| Mindfulness | `/mindfulness` | Push |\n351\t| Settings | `/settings` | Push |\n352\t\n353\t---\n354\t\n355\t## 13. Theme Dependencies\n356\t\n357\tThis screen uses `Theme.of(context)` to access design tokens. The theme is configured via `app_theme.dart` which provides:\n358\t- `ColorScheme` with all palette colors mapped\n359\t- `TextTheme` with Nunito font family\n360\t- `CardTheme` with proper corner radius and elevation"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"75c5ca82-621c-4a88-ac54-a2abec5ee043","uuid":"553bd41e-fd2c-4e2f-8936-e4e88785938a","timestamp":"2026-05-18T23:35:11.315Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/minh/Documents/openplayboosks/examples/baby-app/.stitch/designs/profile/SPEC.md","content":"# Profile Screen Specification\n\n## 1. Screen Title\n\n**Profile**\n\n---\n\n## 2. Purpose\n\nPersonal profile tab serving as a navigation hub to Mindfulness and Settings, with user avatar and name display. Part of the 4-tab bottom navigation shell. This screen provides access to mindfulness resources, app settings, and user profile management.\n\n**Context:** Part of ShellRoute with BottomNavigationBar (4 tabs, index 3). Users arrive here from bottom nav or by tapping the avatar icon on Home AppBar.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Route\n\n`/profile`\n\n---\n\n## 4. Widget Name\n\n`ProfileScreen`\n\n---\n\n## 5. Design Tokens\n\n### Colors (Light Theme)\n\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `lavenderBloom` | `#7C3AED` | Primary brand, active nav indicator, Settings icon |\n| `blushRose` | `#F9A8D4` | Secondary accent, Mindfulness icon |\n| `softMint` | `#6EE7B7` | Tertiary, success states |\n| `morningMist` | `#FAFAFA` | Card backgrounds |\n| `lavenderTint` | `#F5F3FF` | Scaffold background |\n| `deepGraphite` | `#1F2937` | Primary text (titles, names) |\n| `stoneGrey` | `#6B7280` | Secondary text, descriptions |\n| `mistyBorder` | `#E5E7EB` | Card borders if needed |\n| `warmWhite` | `#FFFFFF` | Bottom nav background, card surfaces |\n| `deepTwilight` | `#1E1B2E` | Card backgrounds in dark mode |\n| `twilightBloom` | `#9F67FF` | Primary brand in dark mode |\n| `duskyRose` | `#FBC4E0` | Secondary accent in dark mode |\n| `nightMint` | `#34D399` | Tertiary success in dark mode |\n\n### Colors (Dark Theme)\n\n| Token | Hex | Usage |\n|---|---|---|\n| `twilightBloom` | `#9F67FF` | Primary brand, active nav indicator |\n| `duskyRose` | `#FBC4E0` | Secondary accent, Mindfulness icon |\n| `nightMint` | `#34D399` | Tertiary, success states |\n| `deepTwilight` | `#1E1B2E` | Card backgrounds |\n| `nightSky` | `#13111C` | Scaffold background |\n| `softPearl` | `#F3F4F6` | Primary text |\n| `mutedSilver` | `#9CA3AF` | Secondary text, descriptions |\n| `deepBorder` | `#2D2B3A` | Card borders |\n| `charcoalSurface` | `#252336` | Bottom nav background, card surfaces |\n\n### Typography (Google Fonts — Nunito)\n\n| Style | Size | Weight | Line Height | Usage |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| `displayLarge` | 32sp | 700 | 40sp | User name display |\n| `headlineMedium` | 24sp | 700 | 32sp | Section headers |\n| `titleLarge` | 20sp | 600 | 28sp | AppBar title |\n| `titleMedium` | 16sp | 600 | 24sp | Card titles |\n| `bodyLarge` | 16sp | 400 | 24sp | Body text |\n| `bodyMedium` | 14sp | 400 | 20sp | Secondary text, descriptions |\n| `labelLarge` | 14sp | 600 | 20sp | Button text, chip labels |\n| `caption` | 12sp | 400 | 16sp | Badges, timestamps |\n\n### Spacing Rhythm (base 8dp)\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `xxs` | 4dp |\n| `xs` | 8dp |\n| `sm` | 12dp |\n| `md` | 16dp |\n| `lg` | 24dp |\n| `xl` | 32dp |\n| `xxl` | 48dp |\n\n### Corner Radius\n\n| Token | Value |\n|---|---|\n| `sm` | 8dp |\n| `md` | 12dp |\n| `lg` | 16dp |\n| `full` | 999dp |\n\n### Motion\n\n| Token | Duration | Curve |\n|---|---|---|\n| `durationShort` | 200ms | `Curves.easeOut` |\n| `durationMedium` | 300ms | `Curves.easeInOut` |\n| Stagger delay | 50ms between items | — |\n\n### Elevation\n\n| Token | Usage |\n|---|---|\n| `level0` | Scaffold background |\n| `level1` | Cards, bottom nav |\n| `level2` | FAB, bottom sheets |\n\n---\n\n## 6. Layout Rules\n\n### Scaffold Structure\n\n- `Scaffold` with `SingleChildScrollView` as body (simple card list, no slivers needed)\n- `AppBar`: title \"Profile\", no leading (tab screen), transparent background\n- `BottomNavigationBar`: visible (4 tabs, index 3 = Profile active)\n- No FAB on Profile tab screen\n- Safe area: 12dp top padding for status bar, 80dp bottom for nav + home indicator\n\n### AppBar Behavior\n\n- Transparent background blending to `lavenderTint`\n- Title: \"Profile\" (SemiBold 20sp, `deepGraphite`)\n- No back button (tab screen)\n- No trailing actions\n\n### Body Layout\n\n- `SingleChildScrollView` as body\n- `Padding` with 16dp horizontal\n- `Column` with `mainAxisSize: MainAxisSize.min` containing sections\n- 24dp vertical spacing between sections\n- Bottom padding: 100dp to clear bottom nav\n\n---\n\n## 7. Sections\n\n### Section 1: Profile Header (Avatar + Name)\n\n**Description:** User avatar with gradient background, name, and due date preview.\n\n**Widget Type:** `Column` with centered content, wrapped in `SliverToBoxAdapter`\n\n**Layout:** Centered column at top of scrollable content.\n\n**Components:**\n- Avatar container (80dp diameter) with gradient fill (`lavenderBloom` to `blushRose`)\n- User initial or emoji inside avatar circle\n- User name (`displayLarge`, `deepGraphite`)\n- Due date subtitle (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`) — from `PregnancyProfileProvider`\n- Edit profile button (text button, `lavenderBloom`)\n\n**Data Requirements:**\n- `name` from `UserPreferencesProvider`\n- `dueDate` from `PregnancyProfileProvider`\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap edit profile button → `context.push('/settings')` (Profile section)\n- Tap avatar → no action (decorative)\n\n---\n\n### Section 2: Mindfulness Link Card\n\n**Description:** Navigation card leading to guided breathing exercises and stretching guides.\n\n**Widget:** `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback.\n\n**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, `Row` with icon left, text right, chevron trailing.\n\n**Components:**\n- 48dp circular icon container with `blushRose` at 20% opacity fill\n- Icon: `Icons.self_improvement` (24sp, `blushRose`)\n- Title: \"Mindfulness\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n- Description: \"Breathing exercises, stretching, relaxation\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n- Trailing: `Icons.chevron_right` (24sp, `stoneGrey`)\n\n**Data Requirements:** None (static navigation)\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap card → `context.push('/mindfulness')`\n- Scale feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms return\n\n---\n\n### Section 3: Settings Link Card\n\n**Description:** Navigation card leading to app settings and preferences.\n\n**Widget:** `Card` wrapped in `InkWell` for tap feedback.\n\n**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding, `Row` with icon left, text right, chevron trailing.\n\n**Components:**\n- 48dp circular icon container with `lavenderBloom` at 15% opacity fill\n- Icon: `Icons.settings_outlined` (24sp, `lavenderBloom`)\n- Title: \"Settings\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n- Description: \"Notifications, due date, data export\" (`bodyMedium`, `stoneGrey`)\n- Trailing: `Icons.chevron_right` (24sp, `stoneGrey`)\n\n**Data Requirements:** None (static navigation)\n\n**Interactive Elements:**\n- Tap card → `context.push('/settings')`\n- Scale feedback: 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms return\n\n---\n\n### Section 4: App Info Card (About)\n\n**Description:** Minimal card showing app version.\n\n**Widget:** `Card` (non-interactive, display only).\n\n**Layout:** Full-width card with 16dp internal padding.\n\n**Components:**\n- App name: \"Baby Bump\" (`titleMedium`, `deepGraphite`)\n- Version text: \"Version 1.0.0\" (`caption`, `stoneGrey`)\n- Privacy policy link text button\n\n**Data Requirements:** None (static content)\n\n**Interactive Elements:** None (display only)\n\n---\n\n## 8. Data\n\n### Entities Consumed on This Screen\n\n| Entity | Provider | Fields Used |\n|---|---|---|\n| `UserPreferences` | `UserPreferencesProvider` | `name` |\n| `PregnancyProfile` | `PregnancyProfileProvider` | `dueDate` |\n\n### State Operations\n\n- **Read** `name` for Profile Header display name\n- **Read** `dueDate` for Profile Header due date subtitle\n\n### Provider Integration\n\n```dart\n// In ProfileScreen build method:\nfinal userPrefs = ref.watch(userPreferencesProvider);\nfinal pregnancyProfile = ref.watch(pregnancyProfileProvider);\n```\n\n---\n\n## 9. Motion\n\n### Entry Animations\n\n- Screen loads with fade-in: 300ms, `Curves.easeOut`\n- Header avatar has subtle scale-in: 200ms from 95% to 100%\n- Cards use staggered entry: 100ms delay between each card, 300ms fade per card\n- Total stagger duration: 600ms for all four sections\n\n### Interactive Feedback\n\n- Card tap: 200ms ease-out scale to 98% on press, 200ms ease-out return\n- Bottom nav indicator: 200ms ease-in-out glide between tab positions\n\n### Anti-Motion\n\n- All animations respect `MediaQuery.disableAnimations`\n- `prefers-reduced-motion` media query honored — when enabled, skip all animations\n\n---\n\n## 10. Accessibility\n\n### Semantic Labels\n\n| Element | Semantic Label |\n|---|---|\n| AppBar | `'Profile screen'` |\n| Avatar | `'User profile picture'` |\n| Name display | `'User name: ${userName}'` |\n| Due date display | `'Due date: ${formattedDate}'` |\n| Edit profile button | `'Edit profile, double tap to open settings'` |\n| Mindfulness card | `'Mindfulness, double tap to open mindfulness screen'` |\n| Settings card | `'Settings, double tap to open settings screen'` |\n| Bottom nav items | Built-in semantics from `NavigationBar` |\n\n### Focus Order\n\n1. Avatar circle\n2. User name\n3. Due date subtitle\n4. Edit profile button\n5. Mindfulness card\n6. Settings card\n7. About card\n8. Bottom navigation items (in order: Home, Browse, Library, Profile)\n\n### Contrast Notes\n\n- `lavenderBloom` (#7C3AED) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~5.2:1 (AA compliant)\n- `blushRose` (#F9A8D4) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~3.8:1 (AA borderline — used for icon backgrounds)\n- `deepGraphite` (#1F2937) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~12:1 (AAA compliant)\n- `stoneGrey` (#6B7280) on `morningMist` (#FAFAFA): ~4.7:1 (AA borderline — used for descriptions only)\n- Active bottom nav text uses `lavenderBloom` (5.2:1), inactive uses `stoneGrey` (4.7:1)\n\n### Touch Target Compliance\n\n- All cards: full card area, minimum 56dp height\n- Icon containers: 48dp diameter\n- Edit profile button: 48dp minimum height\n- Avatar: 80dp diameter (decorative, no interaction beyond visual)\n- All interactive elements meet 48dp minimum touch target\n\n### Screen Reader Support\n\n- `AnnounceRouteChange` for tab switches\n- Live region on profile name: \"Profile screen, ${userName}\"\n\n---\n\n## 11. Anti-Patterns\n\n**Do Not:**\n- Add a FAB to Profile tab screen (tab screens don't have FABs per UX.md)\n- Use `CustomScrollView` with slivers (not needed for simple card list — use `SingleChildScrollView`)\n- Add gradients to card backgrounds (flat `morningMist` only for content cards)\n- Use platform default colors (all colors from design system)\n- Use Inter, Roboto, or any font other than Nunito\n- Create touch targets smaller than 48dp\n- Use pure black (#000000) or pure white (#FFFFFF) for text\n- Add more than the 4 defined sections (header, mindfulness, settings, about)\n- Use hero animations (simple push navigation with no shared elements)\n- Add elevation shadows beyond level1 for cards (soft shadow only)\n- Place critical actions below the thumb zone\n- Use hard-coded user name — derive from `UserPreferencesProvider.name`\n\n---\n\n## 12. Navigation Dependencies\n\n| Destination | Route | Navigation Type |\n|---|---|---|\n| Mindfulness | `/mindfulness` | Push |\n| Settings | `/settings` | Push |\n\n---\n\n## 13. Theme Dependencies\n\nThis screen uses `Theme.of(context)` to access design tokens. The theme is configured via `app_theme.dart` which provides:\n- `ColorScheme` with all palette colors mapped\n- `TextTheme` with Nunito font family\n- `CardTheme` with proper corner radius and elevation","numLines":360,"startLine":1,"totalLines":360}}}
